		"inclusion": "ADDING YOUR DEVICE TO A Z-WAVE NETWORK 1. Follow the instructions for your Z-Wave certified controller to add a device to the Z-Wave network. 2. Once the controller is ready to add your device, press and release the manual/program button on the smart switch to add it in the network. 3. The controller’s app will indicate if it has discovered the switch. If prompted by the controller to enter the S2 security code, refer to the QR code/security number on the side of the box or the QR code label on the product (see Figure 1). Enter the 5-digit code",
